RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT distinct a.contract_ref_no, b.user_ref_no, x.counterparty, x.CONTRACT_CCY, y.principal_outstanding_bal, z.short_name from OLTB_CONTRACT_MASTER a, oltbs_contract b, oltb_contract x, oltb_contract_balance y, OLTMS_CUSTOMER z where a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_reF_no and a.version_no = b.latest_version_no and x.counterparty = z.customer_no and sypks_utils.get_branch(A.CONTRACT_REF_NO) = global.current_branch and nvl(a.cascade_participation,'Y') = 'Y' and b.contract_status = 'A' and b.auth_status = 'A' and b.module_code = 'OL' and x.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no and x.contracT_status = 'A' and x.contract_ref_no = y.contract_ref_no and x.product_type = 'C' and exists (SELECT contract_ref_no FROM oltbs_contract_linkages l WHERE l.linked_to_ref = a.contract_ref_no AND l.linkage_valid='Y' AND l.linkage_type='C')

select a.customer_no, b.short_name from OLVWS_PRODUCT_CUSTOMERS a, oltms_customer b where a.product_code = ? and a.customer_no = b.customer_no and b.auth_stat = 'A' and b.record_stat = 'O' order by a.customer_no

select a.product_code, a.product_description from oltms_product a, OLVWS_AVAILABLE_PRODBR b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLTMS_PRODUCT_ROLLOVER d where a.module = 'OL' and a.product_code = b.product_code and a.product_code = c.product and a.product_code = d.product and c.product_type = 'L' and c.rollover_allowed = 'Y' and d.rollover_method = 'C' and b.branch_code = global.current_branch and b.user_id = global.user_id order by a.product_code

select vw.ccy_code, ccy.ccy_name from olvws_product_currencies vw, cytms_ccy_defn ccy where vw.ccy_code = ccy.ccy_code and vw.product_code = ? and ccy.record_stat = 'O' and ccy.auth_stat = 'A' order by vw.ccy_code

SELECT DRAWDOWN_NO FROM LBTBS_DRAWDOWN_SCHEDULE WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO = ? and DRAWDOWN_TYPE = 'R' and RENEWAL_TYPE = 'C' and nvl(associated,'N')='N' and drawdown_ccy = ? and borrower = ? and drawdown_date = ? MINUS SELECT DRAWDOWN_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_CONSOL_MASTER WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO = ?

select a.contract_ref_no from oltb_contract a, oltb_contract_master b where a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no and a.latest_version_no = b.version_no and a.module_code = 'OL' and a.product_code = ? and a.counterparty = ? and a.contract_ccy = ? and a.auth_status = 'A' and b.product_type = 'L' and b.maturity_date >= ? and b.contract_status = 'A' and b.rollover_method = 'C' and exists (select contract_ref_no from oltb_contract_linkages c where c.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no and c.version_no = a.latest_version_no and c.linked_to_ref = ? and c.linked_to_branch = global.current_branch and c.linkage_valid = 'Y' and c.linkage_type = 'C') MINUS select participant_ref_no from oltb_contract_consol_detail

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: CONTRACT_REF_NO IN (select contract_ref_no from OLTB_CONTRACT_CONSOL_MASTER) and branch=global.current_branch and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: CONTRACT_REF_NO IN (select contract_ref_no from OLTB_CONTRACT_CONSOL_MASTER) and Branch IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID) and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select a.product_code, a.product_description from oltms_product a, OLVWS_AVAILABLE_PRODBR b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLTMS_PRODUCT_ROLLOVER d where a.module = 'OL' and a.product_code = b.product_code and a.product_code = c.product and a.product_code = d.product and c.product_type = 'L' and c.rollover_allowed = 'Y' and d.rollover_method = 'C' and b.branch_code = global.current_branch and b.user_id = global.user_id and b.product_code in (select product_code from (select a.contract_ref_no,a.product_code from oltb_contract a, oltb_contract_master b where a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no and a.latest_version_no = b.version_no and a.module_code = 'OL' and a.counterparty = ? and a.contract_ccy = ? and a.auth_status = 'A' and b.product_type = 'L' and b.maturity_date >= ? and b.contract_status = 'A' and b.rollover_method = 'C' and exists (select contract_ref_no from oltb_contract_linkages c where c.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no and c.version_no = a.latest_version_no and c.linked_to_ref = ? and c.linked_to_branch = global.current_branch and c.linkage_valid = 'Y' and c.linkage_type = 'C') MINUS select participant_ref_no, sypks_utils.get_product(PARTICIPANT_REF_NO) product_code from oltb_contract_consol_detail))order by a.product_code

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.CONTRACT_REF_NO=LFTBS_CONT_ADDL_INT_DTL.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.VERSION_NO = LFTBS_CONT_ADDL_INT_DTL.VERSION_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.SPLIT_NO = LFTBS_CONT_ADDL_INT_DTL.SPLIT_SERIAL_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.COMPONENT = LFTBS_CONT_ADDL_INT_DTL.COMPONENT

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT B.RATE_CODE, B.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE B WHERE B.BRANCH_CODE = ? AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
